import React, { Component } from 'react'; import { BrowserRouter as Router } from 'react-router-dom'; import { connect } from 'react-redux'; import AppRouter from './config/router'; import 'antd/dist/antd.css'; import * as actions from './store/actions/auth'; class App extends Component { render() { return (
); } } const mapStateToProps = state => { return { isAuthenticated: state.token !== null } }; const mapDispatchToProps = dispatch => { return { onTryAutoSignup: () => dispatch(actions.authCheckState()) } }; export default connect(mapStateToProps, mapDispatchToProps)(App);
